Interface DataProviderI

  • All Superinterfaces:

    public interface DataProviderI
extends fr.upmc.components.interfaces.RequiredI, fr.upmc.components.interfaces.OfferedI
    This interface DataProviderI list the signature of methods to be implemented in the Class DateProvider which collects the infos about the Computers and Applications on the DataCenter
